name: Cryptocurrency Logos and Icons
description:
The design asset library of icons and logos fueling the open source React component cryptocurrency icon library called Cryptocons.


  • If you want optimized SVG versions of these check out the folder in the repository
  • If you want to use them as React Components, check out the website
  • If you want to contribute icons, that would be awesome. Send me a link to your Figma file on Twitter
